    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Bonus Action, you can spend 1 <strong>Actualization Die</strong> when you would cast a Genjutsu of at least C-Rank or lower. When you do, if the Genjutsu requires you to roll dice to deal damage, heal, increase/reduce damage reduction or provide temporary hit points. You add the actualization die to the roll, interpreting the results as normal.</p>",
